{"slide_id": "4d21131e737edf33a8cf5d1376403ede-20220308_Open_C__s5__G1_TEXT_OVERFLOW", "width": 960, "height": 540, "elements": [{"element_id": "shp325", "type": "image", "bbox": {"x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "width": 958.41, "height": 540.0}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 0, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp326", "type": "title", "bbox": {"x": 32.72, "y": 46.72, "width": 894.55, "height": 60.13}, "text": "How YOU can Get Involved:", "style": {"font_size_pt": 26.0}, "z": 1, "placeholder_id": "TITLE (1)", "metadata": {"role": "TITLE (1)"}}, {"element_id": "shp327", "type": "body", "bbox": {"x": 32.72, "y": 113.56, "width": 834.39, "height": 270.24}, "text": "To implement a cultural shift, we need community engagement from the broad spectrum across the scientific community!\nWe are looking for community partners to co-develop YOOS activities \nHost and fund prizes and challenges,\nOpen, online open science curricula development,\nGovernance framework structures to develop open science action plans for science teams across agencies and institutions,\nBudget for YOOS activities to support open science learning and funding requirements across science teams", "style": {"font_size_pt": 16.0}, "z": 2, "placeholder_id": "BODY (2)", "metadata": {"role": "BODY (2)"}}, {"element_id": "shp328", "type": "shape", "bbox": {"x": 32.72, "y": 104.99, "width": 808.85, "height": 1.39}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 3, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp329", "type": "shape", "bbox": {"x": 685.59, "y": 494.06, "width": 36.03, "height": 17.7}, "text": "", "style": {"fill_color": "#001D38"}, "z": 4, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp330", "type": "image", "bbox": {"x": -0.0, "y": 524.86, "width": 43.26, "height": 15.14}, "text": "", "style": {}, "z": 5, "placeholder_id": null, "metadata": {}}, {"element_id": "shp331", "type": "body", "bbox": {"x": 198.69, "y": 390.5, "width": 738.2, "height": 113.92}, "text": "Learn more 